        jTextArea1.setText("Prestige Wheels, established in October 2022, has distinguished itself in the\ncompetitive market through its unwavering commitment to integrity, transparency, \nand customer satisfaction. Our headquarters and showroom are conveniently located\nin Sabang, Lipa City, serving customers both from outside Batangas and within the\nprovince");
